16
00:01:12,114 --> 00:01:16,785
[KASUMI laughing]

17
00:01:16,868 --> 00:01:18,787
[KASUMI'S MOTHER]
All right.

18
00:01:18,870 --> 00:01:20,872
Let's give that poor
child a good home.

19
00:01:23,667 --> 00:01:26,420
