22
00:01:34,177 --> 00:01:35,721
[KASUMI'S FATHER]
Yes, that's right,

23
00:01:35,804 --> 00:01:37,639
and he's going to be
part of our family,

24
00:01:37,723 --> 00:01:40,017
so be sure to treat him well.

25
00:01:42,227 --> 00:01:43,437
Go ahead, darling.

26
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,855
Say hello to him.

27
00:01:48,108 --> 00:01:49,985
Hello, I'm Kasumi.

28
00:01:52,738 --> 00:01:53,739
