our twisted story began.

37
00:02:15,969 --> 00:02:19,306
[MERCURIUS] And now, beloved
factor of self‐destruction.

38
00:02:19,389 --> 00:02:21,433
I will share with you
the requisite conditions

39
00:02:21,516 --> 00:02:23,352
to be the star of the show.

40
00:02:25,604 --> 00:02:28,065
[MERCURIUS] One of
God's featured playthings.

41
00:04:13,253 --> 00:04:14,880
[MERCURIUS]
Every man has his own path

42
00:04:14,963 --> 00:04:17,466
that fate leads him down.

43
00:04:17,549 --> 00:04:19,968
For example, there are those
hunters who are destined

44
00:04:20,051 --> 00:04:22,512
to always have their
favorite quarry stolen out

45
00:04:22,596 --> 00:04:24,389
from under them.

46
00:04:24,473 --> 00:04:27,309
