104
00:07:27,697 --> 00:07:30,075
Put simply, both of your
childhood friends were born

105
00:07:30,158 --> 00:07:31,660
as a result of
decades of planning

106
00:07:31,743 --> 00:07:33,620
and genetic coordination.

107
00:07:33,703 --> 00:07:35,705
