124
00:08:17,747 --> 00:08:19,165
what was happening to him,

125
00:08:19,249 --> 00:08:21,209
Kasumi would have
been devastated.

126
00:08:21,292 --> 00:08:23,503
Thus, when he decided
to suffer in silence,

127
00:08:23,586 --> 00:08:25,171
his feelings were genuine.

128
00:08:25,255 --> 00:08:28,883
But all things have
front and back sides.

129
00:08:28,967 --> 00:08:33,847
His wish to destroy his false,
everyday life was also genuine.

130
00:08:33,930 --> 00:08:36,266
However, you were
able to take its place.

131
00:08:36,349 --> 00:08:39,978
To both rescue it
and destroy it.

132
00:08:40,061 --> 00:08:42,397
Just as my dear friend
is to me...

133
00:08:42,480 --> 00:08:45,316
You, the manifestation
of the urge for ruination,

134
00:08:45,400 --> 00:08:47,444
the self‐destruction factor.

135
00:08:47,527 --> 00:08:50,447
That is the role you must play.

136
00:08:50,530 --> 00:08:51,990
I will not allow you to die

137
00:08:52,073 --> 00:08:53,950
as long as you are useful to me,

138
00:08:54,034 --> 00:08:56,911
and as long as you don't
overextend your déjà vu.

139
00:08:56,995 --> 00:09:00,123
Show me the unforeseen
conclusion I've longed for.

140
00:09:00,206 --> 00:09:02,542
That is the reason I've gifted
you with such incredible

141
00:09:02,625 --> 00:09:04,335
power and uncanny luck.

142
00:09:05,628 --> 00:09:08,048
[SHIROU laughing]

143
