of a dick, but Ren isn't!

150
00:09:22,395 --> 00:09:26,024
His friendship with you is
both true and important.

151
00:09:26,107 --> 00:09:28,610
And you can be certain the
feelings I have for my friend

152
00:09:28,693 --> 00:09:31,029
and counterpart are exactly
the same as the ones

153
00:09:31,112 --> 00:09:33,198
my son holds for you.

154
00:09:33,281 --> 00:09:35,825
