157
00:09:40,622 --> 00:09:43,750
we always build a
destructive relationship.

158
00:09:43,833 --> 00:09:45,376
As you know,

159
00:09:45,460 --> 00:09:47,003
from the moment you
picked up that blade,

160
00:09:47,087 --> 00:09:49,631
you brought his
normal life to an end.

161
00:09:56,346 --> 00:09:58,264
[MERCURIUS]
Which brings us here.

162
00:09:58,348 --> 00:10:01,684
I am hoping that you choose
to disrupt things once again.

163
00:10:01,768 --> 00:10:03,394
