254
00:14:19,609 --> 00:14:21,903
and remember, I alone know you.

255
00:14:21,986 --> 00:14:24,989
The one my love causes to rot.

256
00:14:28,493 --> 00:14:30,370
[WILHELM]
Briah!

257
00:14:34,290 --> 00:14:39,087
[WILHELM]
Rosenkavalier Schwarzwald!

258
00:14:53,976 --> 00:14:55,061
Here we go!

259
00:14:57,563 --> 00:15:01,067
[RUSALKA yelling]

260
00:15:01,150 --> 00:15:04,862
I don't want to die.
I don't want to die.

261
00:15:04,946 --> 00:15:06,489
I don't want to die.
I don't want to die!

262
00:15:06,572 --> 00:15:09,826
I don't want to die!
I don't want to die!

263
00:15:09,909 --> 00:15:11,494
I don't want to die!

264
00:15:12,328 --> 00:15:15,581
[RUSALKA gasping]

265
00:15:15,665 --> 00:15:17,041
That's it.

266
00:15:17,125 --> 00:15:19,752
I'll be like her
before much longer.

267
00:15:19,836 --> 00:15:22,213
If so, then I'll just...

268
00:15:24,257 --> 00:15:25,216
[REA gasps]

269
00:15:25,299 --> 00:15:30,054
[RUSALKA screaming]

270
00:15:32,557 --> 00:15:33,766
[RUSALKA]
God, no!

271
00:15:40,314 --> 00:15:42,066
[RUSALKA gasping]

272
00:15:44,318 --> 00:15:45,987
[RUSALKA gasping]

273
00:15:50,283 --> 00:15:53,870
[growls]

274
00:15:55,788 --> 00:15:57,582
[RUSALKA gasps]

275
00:15:59,250 --> 00:16:00,710
[WOLFGANG]
Hello, Anna.

276
00:16:00,793 --> 00:16:02,545
Been a while, hasn't it?

277
00:16:02,628 --> 00:16:04,505
Just like old times.

278
00:16:04,589 --> 00:16:06,507
What? Is that you?

279
00:16:06,591 --> 00:16:07,633
Schreiber...

280
00:16:09,343 --> 00:16:11,095
Schreiber, you have to help!

281
00:16:11,179 --> 00:16:13,556
Please!
I think I'm going to die!

282
00:16:19,020 --> 00:16:20,480
No, wait!

283
00:16:20,563 --> 00:16:21,647
Please don't go!

284
00:16:21,731 --> 00:16:23,149
I love you, Schreiber!

285
00:16:23,232 --> 00:16:26,110
You can't just leave
me behind to die!

286
00:16:26,194 --> 00:16:27,528
[WOLFGANG]
I never knew.

287
00:16:27,612 --> 00:16:29,947
You love me? Really?

288
00:16:30,031 --> 00:16:32,158
Ja. So please, darling.

289
00:16:32,241 --> 00:16:34,327
I need your help now!

290
00:16:34,410 --> 00:16:36,078
I don't want to die.

291
00:16:36,162 --> 00:16:38,414
I want to live.
You and I together!

292
00:16:38,498 --> 00:16:40,166
Because I love you!

293
00:16:45,046 --> 00:16:46,881
[WOLFGANG]
I understand.

294
00:16:46,964 --> 00:16:48,841
I just never knew.

295
00:16:50,343 --> 00:16:53,304
Anna. I love you, too.

296
00:16:53,387 --> 00:16:55,139
I'm happy.

297
00:16:55,223 --> 00:16:57,016
Promise that you'll
always protect me‐‐

298
00:16:57,099 --> 00:16:59,060
[gasping]

299
00:17:03,189 --> 00:17:08,736
[WOLFGANG laughing]

300
00:17:08,819 --> 00:17:10,071
It's wonderful!

301
00:17:10,154 --> 00:17:11,906
I love the way this feels!

302
00:17:11,989 --> 00:17:14,158
I never knew what I was missing!

303
00:17:14,242 --> 00:17:15,910
I'll slaughter the
beast that did this

304
00:17:15,993 --> 00:17:17,286
to my <i>liebchen</i> !

305
00:17:17,370 --> 00:17:19,121
So tragically poignant!

306
00:17:19,205 --> 00:17:21,749
And yet dreadfully romantic!

307
00:17:21,832 --> 00:17:23,334
My love!

308
00:17:23,417 --> 00:17:26,629
I've never killed anyone
for this reason before!

309
00:17:26,712 --> 00:17:28,089
I will avenge you.

310
00:17:28,172 --> 00:17:31,425
You may die,
but our love never will!

311
00:17:31,509 --> 00:17:36,013
[laughing]

312
00:17:57,451 --> 00:17:58,661
[WILHELM yells]

313
00:18:06,085 --> 00:18:07,753
[HELGA laughing]

314
00:18:07,837 --> 00:18:09,922
[HELGA] What do you think
you're doing, miscreant?

315
00:18:10,006 --> 00:18:11,882
Leave my dear Wilhelm be!

316
00:18:16,887 --> 00:18:18,973
[WILHELM] You two haven't
met yet, have you?

317
00:18:20,182 --> 00:18:21,309
[WILHELM chuckles]

318
00:18:22,560 --> 00:18:24,770
[WILHELM]
Allow me to introduce Helga.

319
00:18:24,854 --> 00:18:26,814
Both my sister and my mother.

320
00:18:37,658 --> 00:18:40,077
[HELGA]
Villi. Villi.

321
00:18:40,161 --> 00:18:42,955
Oh my treasured
little boy, Vilhelm!

322
00:18:43,039 --> 00:18:45,666
I won't let anyone
be cruel to you.

323
00:18:45,750 --> 00:18:49,128
And if they are, kill them‐‐
butcher every last one!

324
00:18:49,211 --> 00:18:52,131
[WILHELM] Ja, she can
be a bit overprotective.

325
00:18:52,214 --> 00:18:55,509
Whenever I get too
excitable, she comes out.

326
00:18:55,593 --> 00:18:59,263
Goddamn, you really are
one crazy motherfucker!

327
00:18:59,347 --> 00:19:01,891
Don't you dare speak
that way to my son!

328
00:19:06,228 --> 00:19:08,105
[HELGA laughing]

329
00:19:20,576 --> 00:19:22,370
[WILHELM yells]

330
00:19:24,246 --> 00:19:25,456
[SHIROU gasps]

331
00:19:35,966 --> 00:19:38,886
[WILHELM laughing]

332
00:19:38,969 --> 00:19:41,222
I love it! Keep the
good stuff coming, kid!

333
00:19:41,305 --> 00:19:43,140
I want more, so don't stop!

334
00:19:43,224 --> 00:19:45,601
That was all right
for an appetizer,

335
00:19:45,685 --> 00:19:47,812
but now it's time
for the main course.

336
00:19:47,895 --> 00:19:49,647
Yeah?

337
00:19:49,730 --> 00:19:51,524
Well save room for the
ass‐kicking I'm serving ya!

338
00:19:54,527 --> 00:19:57,905
[WILHELM grunting]

339
00:19:59,448 --> 00:20:00,533
[WILHELM]
Schreiber?

340
00:20:00,616 --> 00:20:02,118
Let me go!

341
00:20:02,201 --> 00:20:03,411
[WOLFGANG]
Quiet down.

342
00:20:03,494 --> 00:20:04,995
You're in my way.

343
00:20:05,079 --> 00:20:07,289
I think it's about
time you got lost.

344
00:20:07,373 --> 00:20:09,709
I'm here for him.

345
00:20:13,796 --> 00:20:16,757
[WILHELM yelling]

346
00:20:21,345 --> 00:20:24,890
[WILHELM]
Not yet! No!

347
00:20:39,321 --> 00:20:40,364
[WOLFGANG chuckles]

348
00:20:41,198 --> 00:20:43,451
I must say you've surprised me.

349
00:20:43,534 --> 00:20:45,703
I can't believe Bey
lost to you like that.

350
00:20:45,786 --> 00:20:48,414
I swear, I never would have
imagined that outcome.

351
00:20:48,497 --> 00:20:50,458
Look, you're the one
who killed him, Patch.

352
00:20:50,541 --> 00:20:52,501
That's not important.

353
00:20:52,585 --> 00:20:55,296
You're responsible
for this, yeah?

354
00:20:55,379 --> 00:20:58,215
I guess our love was like
ships passing in the night,

355
00:20:58,299 --> 00:21:00,509
but I still have to
avenge her death.

356
00:21:00,593 --> 00:21:03,554
So I'm going to kill you
for what you did.

357
00:21:03,637 --> 00:21:05,306
[RUSALKA]
Help me.

358
00:21:05,389 --> 00:21:07,057
Please, help me.

359
00:21:07,141 --> 00:21:08,350
It hurts.

360
00:21:08,434 --> 00:21:10,269
Please, Schreiber.

361
00:21:10,352 --> 00:21:11,645
I don't want to die‐‐

362
00:21:16,442 --> 00:21:18,986
Once she's dead,
I will seek my revenge.

363
00:21:19,069 --> 00:21:21,238
Run away while you still can.

364
00:21:21,322 --> 00:21:22,907
It doesn't matter
where you hide.

365
00:21:22,990 --> 00:21:25,993
I'll find you,
and then rip you to pieces.

366
00:21:26,076 --> 00:21:28,996
[WOLFGANG laughing]

367
00:21:31,540 --> 00:21:33,125
We'll meet again soon.

368
00:21:33,209 --> 00:21:36,420
You have the word
of Wolfgang Schreiber:

369
00:21:36,504 --> 00:21:38,964
<i>Einherjar</i> of Lord Heydrich!

370
00:21:39,048 --> 00:21:43,469
A fallen warrior lifted by
valkyries into golden Valhalla!

371
00:21:43,552 --> 00:21:47,598
[WOLFGANG laughing]

